```mermaid
graph TD
    Client["User's Browser"] -->|1. DNS Request| DNS["DNS Server"]
    DNS -->|2. Returns IP| Client
    Client -->|3. Connects to IP:443 (HTTPS)| Firewall["Firewall"]
    Firewall -->|4. Passes encrypted traffic| LoadBalancer["Load Balancer"]
    LoadBalancer -->|5. Routes request| WebServer["Web Server (Nginx)"]
    WebServer -->|6. Passes request| AppServer["Application Server"]
    AppServer -->|7. Queries| Database["Database (MySQL)"]
    Database -->|8. Returns data| AppServer
    AppServer -->|9. Generates page| WebServer
    WebServer -->|10. Serves page| Client
